.containter.col-md-offset-1
  .row.container
    %h2#features Key Features

    .col-md-5.col-sm-5.features
      .create_slideshows
        %b Create Slideshows
        %p Create slideshows quickly and easily.

      .add_images
        %b Add Images As Slides
        %p Use the images on your iPhone, iPod Touch or iPad or take new ones to use in your slideshow.

      .record_narrations
        %b Record Narrations
        %p Record a narration for your slideshow. SonicPics synchronizes your images to your recorded audio.

      .intuitive_interface
        %b Intuitive Interface
        %p SonicPics is simple to use. As a user put it "It's clean, simple and intuitive."

    .col-md-5.col-sm-5.features.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-offset-1
      .playback
        %b Playback Recordings On Your Device
        %p Play your recorded slideshows on your iPad, iPhone or iPod Touch.
      .share_recordings
        %b Share Recorded Slideshows Online
        %p Publish your recorded slideshows to YouTube, share to your computer via wifi, or email to your friends.
      .video_out
        %b Supports Video Out
        %p Project your images as you record and then share the recording on an external display.
      .universal_app
        %b Universal App
        %p SonicPics now runs NATIVELY on your iPhone, iPod Touch and iPad.


