      %p.lead Take photos of your kids, special events, weddings, vacations, the new pet, or first day at camp and narrate them with SonicPics!
      %p.lead Narrate your photos like never before, flipping to each image as you are ready to talk. You choose the timing. SonicPics makes it easy to make slideshow movies on your iPod touch or iPhone.
      %p.lead When the recording is complete, publish your movie to your YouTube account or to your computer (wifi required).




